1. *Osobe* u biblioteci su tihe. (People in the library are quiet.)
2. *Osoba* koja je odgovorna za ovaj projekat je on. (The person responsible for this project is him.)
3. *Osobi* nije trebalo dugo da shvati. (It didn't take long for the person to understand.)
4. Prva *osoba* koja je stigla je bila on. (The first person who arrived was him.)
